.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#ls--block-size'\fB\-\-block\-size=SIZE\fP\X'tty: link'
with \fB\-l\fR, scale sizes by SIZE when printing them;
e.g., '\-\-block\-size=M'; see SIZE format below
.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#ls-B'\fB\-B, \-\-ignore\-backups\fP\X'tty: link'
