.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#ls-c'\fB\-c\fP\X'tty: link'
with \fB\-lt\fR: sort by, and show, ctime
(time of last change of file status information);
with \fB\-l\fR: show ctime and sort by name;
otherwise: sort by ctime, newest first
.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#ls-C'\fB\-C\fP\X'tty: link'
list entries by columns
.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#ls--color'\fB\-\-color[=WHEN]\fP\X'tty: link'
color the output WHEN; more info below
.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#ls-d'\fB\-d, \-\-directory\fP\X'tty: link'
