.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#ls--dereference-command-line-symlink-to-dir'\fB\-\-dereference\-command\-line\-symlink\-to\-dir\fP\X'tty: link'
follow each command line symbolic link that points to a directory
.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#ls--hide'\fB\-\-hide=PATTERN\fP\X'tty: link'
do not list implied entries matching shell PATTERN
