.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#ls--indicator-style'\fB\-\-indicator\-style=WORD\fP\X'tty: link'
append indicator with style WORD to entry names:
none (default), slash (\fB\-p\fR), file\-type (\fB\-\-file\-type\fR), classify (\fB\-F\fR)
.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#ls-i'\fB\-i, \-\-inode\fP\X'tty: link'
