.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#ls-t'\fB\-t\fP\X'tty: link'
sort by time, newest first; see \fB\-\-time\fR
.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#ls-T'\fB\-T, \-\-tabsize=\,COLS\fP\X'tty: link'\/\fR
