.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#ls-w'\fB\-w, \-\-width=\,COLS\fP\X'tty: link'\/\fR
set output width to COLS.  0 means no limit
.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#ls-x'\fB\-x\fP\X'tty: link'
list entries by lines instead of by columns
.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#ls-X'\fB\-X\fP\X'tty: link'
sort alphabetically by entry extension
.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#ls-Z'\fB\-Z, \-\-context\fP\X'tty: link'
